title: Shooter Fires at Crowds in Sydney's Bondi Beach
description: Warning: Graphic Images. A video provided to Bloomberg shows a shooter opening fire in Sydney's Bondi Beach area. At least 13 people were killed including a suspected shooter, and several more were injured in what police called a terrorist attack. (Source: Bloomberg)
